{"tid":1534868,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"是否可以向法庭申請禁制令，禁止軍裝警員隱藏個人身份？(蒙面、藏起警員編號等)","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T09:46:54.000Z","uid":264806,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"69c311e9971ab38210979142077933023d992efd","tid":1534868,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:52:40.000Z","msg":"越來越多警員濫用暴力。最近一單係，街坊喺街邊大嗌問警員仲有無良心，然後就有不知名警務人員跑過去扑佢頭及拉左佢。(街坊當時並無武器或危險品)<br />\n<br />\n呢單只係其中一單個案。仲有好多濫用暴力例子。<br />\n<br />\n如果警員仍舊可以隱藏個人身份(蒙面、藏起警員編號等)，呢類濫用暴力既事件將會無日無之。到時市民自保自衛既手段可能會提升，引發更嚴重既暴力衝突。<br />\n<br />\n因此，是否可以向法庭申請禁制令，禁止軍裝警員隱藏個人身份(蒙面、藏起警員編號等)，以避免情況惡化？"},{"pid":"a45355ce342a311bf4143e6b9a168e1ff2a9ea61","tid":1534868,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:52:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dc3391e8bf24b61758caaf8d774b81b63ef3706","tid":1534868,"uid":86416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:58:59.000Z","msg":"推比法律L睇"},{"pid":"f151f9d4965af78534